</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_24" id="12r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Reinhart<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> zu Hanaw
                    </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr edel
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat, wie ir
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> habt, daz der
                                <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan> durlewhtigst fürst und
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Sig<ex>mund</ex></expan>, <expan>römisch<ex>er</ex></expan> und zu
                                <expan>Ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etc. künig,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, gen Speyr <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                        niht lank da <expan>beleibe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan>, und begert, daz wir
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>bottsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> zu seinen <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        tun von der <expan>mutu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>jerlich<ex>er</ex></expan> gült, die ir maint, die ewch auf der
                                <expan>jerlich<ex>en</ex></expan> stewr bey uns
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben,</ex></expan> wan ir ewr
                                <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> auch zu im tun wellet etc., das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Tun wir <pb facs="#facs_25" id="12v"/>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell ze <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz
                        wir <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> frewnd und
                            <expan>ratgesell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Sebolten
                            <expan>Pfinczi<ex>n</ex>g</expan> und <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        Volkmeir zu dem <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, dem <expan>römisch<ex>en</ex></expan> künig,
                        von <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> sache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        gesant <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> ee daz uns ewr brief
                                <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> ist. Den
                            <expan>selb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>frewnd<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>verschr<ex>eiben,</ex></expan> mit
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell oder mit den
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> davon ze reden. Und
                            <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr edel
                            <expan>fleiszikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>, daz ir uns
                                <expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>mutu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> und <expan>vordru<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>tragen</expan> wellet, wan wir niht wissen, daz wir ewch
                        ichts schuldig <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> anthaisz
                            <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan> sein, und daz ir
                            <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> ewch gen
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>frewnd<ex>en</ex></expan> so gnediklich darinn beweiset, als wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell wol getrawn. Möcht
                                <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> des niht gesein, so
                                <expan>süll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> die
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> frewnde die sache von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> für den <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, den <expan>römisch<ex>en</ex></expan> künig,
                                <expan>bring<ex>en</ex></expan> und mit
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> mit den
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> vor <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> zu austrag <expan>kome<ex>n,</ex></expan>
<expan>alsv<ex>er</ex>re</expan> sie <expan>mug<ex>en</ex></expan>. Denn wo
                        wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        dienst etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                        <expan>s<ex>upra.</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
